pe Iisus.

223
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:31,200
Vreau sa-l aleg
pe Iisus.

224
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:38,200
Am gasit ceva!

225
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:22,320
Alegerile din martie
din Calabria,

226
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:24,400
O testare...

227
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:11,280
Ce tratare!

228
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:18,120
-Du-te in pat,mama.
-Nu,sunt bine aici.

229
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:29,560
Am visat ca mi-au
cazut dintii.

230
00:26:31,760 --> 00:26:34,080
Semn rau,asa-i?

231
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:38,280
Destul.

232
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:41,640
Hai aici.

233
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:55,360
Colegii de Confirmare
sunt draguti?

234
00:26:55,560 --> 00:26:58,400
-Normal.
-Asta-i bine.

235
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:02,320
-Ce?
-Ca nu sunt anormali.

236
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:07,400
-Ce faceti?
-Cantam.

237
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:11,760
-Lasa-ma aici.
-Nu-mi amintesc.

238
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,640
Hai,un pic!

239
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:16,400
-Nu,hai...
-Esti jenata?

240
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:19,560
Esti jenata.

241
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:24,480
Hai,un pic,pentru
mama ta ce trebuie
sa mearga la
serviciu.

242
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:31,080
Bine,dar inchide
ochii.

243
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:34,160
Chiar inchide-i!

244
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:47,480
Vreau sa-l aleg
pe Iisus!

245
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:52,680
Vreau sa aleg...

246
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:02,800
-Oh,Doamne!
-De ce esti asa
de egoista?

247
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:07,760
Las-o pe mama sa
doarma.

248
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:12,640
-Tu dormi noaptea,
asa-i?
-Rosetta,ma pot apara
si singura.

249
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:15,680
Nu-i adevarat,

250
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:19,960
Nu realizezi ca-ti
consuma toata
energia.

251
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:24,680
-Iti suge tot ce
ai inauntru!
-Ce tot spui?

252
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:34,120
Astea suny hainele
de Confirmare,

253
00:28:34,320 --> 00:28:36,720
Sunt ale sorei
lui Alfri,

254
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:39,920
Trebuie sa le
inapoiem intacte.

255
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:44,840
Te rog!

256
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:13,040
-Rita,unde ai fost?
-Scuza-ma,fetele...

257
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:18,080
Acum e bine.Aluatul
e pe cale sa creasca!
Ajuta-l.

258
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:45,040
Erau chiar mainile
lui Iius...

259
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:48,640
...Ce-au aratat
sfintenia lui
lumii.

260
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:54,040
Cu mainile,Iisus a
facut prima sa
minune,asa...

261
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:03,760
A inghetat?

262
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:10,560
Si voi puteti
experimenta
acesta energie
a credintei...

263
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:15,240
...Ca Iisus cu
mainile noastre.
Si acum vom face
um joc numit

264
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:17,760
"Dansul omului
nacut orb."

265
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:21,280
-Cine poate spune
cine a fost?
-Eu! Eu!

266
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:25,560
-Anna?
-Orbul era un om ce
n-a vazut niciodata,

267
00:30:25,760 --> 00:30:29,080
-Asa ca Iisus Cristos
i-a dat vedere.
-Bine.

268
00:30:29,280 --> 00:30:33,840
-Cum a facut asta,Jasmine?
-Nu stiu!

269
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,880
-Cinzia?
-Cu mainile?

270
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:40,680
-Mainile.Cum,Sara?
-Le-a pus pe fata
LUI.

271
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,760
Va explic ce-a
facut imediat.

272
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:50,040
Jesus a folosit saliva,
saliva de pe mainil
sale...

273
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:56,080
... Si apoi si le-a
pus pe omul nascut
orb.

274
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:10,720
Stai,imi amintesc
una.

275
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,560
Care?

276
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:18,880
Iisuse,ia-ma in
mainile tale deseara,
si vegheaza-ma pana
la ceasul diminetii.

277
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:23,000
-Nu,nu-i o rugaciune.
-Dar ce-i?
-O fraza.

278
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:26,760
Tin minte toate
rugaciunile ce
exista:

279
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:31,400
Crezul Agoniei,
Crezul Mortii,

280
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:35,680
-Crezul Suferintei...
-Ce minunat!

281
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:41,280
Mama?

282
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:43,680
Treci sub.

283
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:48,800
-Da?
-Odihneste-te,nu
te te obosi.

284
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:51,440
Ma duc la Alfri.

285
00:34:59,200 --> 00:35:03,320
-Sunt un suferind...
-Hai,inceteaza!

286
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:06,520
Hai,inceteaza!

287
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:10,480
Hai,se poate
intoarce!

288
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:12,480
Sa dormim.

289
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:26,480
Ma rog pentru
muribunzi...

290
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:29,680
Ajunge,acum chiar
odihneste-te.

291
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:40,800
Cipsuri,prod. de
patiserie,biscuiti,
prajituri...

292
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,360
Lipsesc bauturile.

293
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:48,240
Daca trebuie sa
luam bauturi,
cheltuielile
cresc,asa-i?

294
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,640
-Parinte Mario?
-Ce-i?

295
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:54,440
Scuzati-ma ca interup
idila asta cu bauturi
si cipsuri.

296
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:57,200
Suntem mai rai
decat copiii!

297
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,080
Se gandesc doar
la haine.

298
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:02,680
-Cine rvine dupa
Confirmare?
-Adulti.

299
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:05,040
Biserica e mereu
plina.Desigur,nu
sunt multi tineri.

300
00:36:05,240 --> 00:36:08,360
Dar noi suntem
mereu aici.

301
00:36:10,600 --> 00:36:15,400
Daca copiii aia merg
la Confirmare,

302
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:17,600
Nu-i putin lucru.

303
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:22,160
-...Trebuie sa invete,
sa creasca...
-Sa creasca,asta-i
cuvantul corect!

304
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:26,600
-N-am vrut nimic.
-Biserica a devenit
un loc

305
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:30,920
Pentru copii,femei,
doamne in varsta
oameni care n-au
nimic de facut.

306
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:36,960
-Cred ca esti pesimista.
-Scuze,poate nu m-a,
exprimat foarte bine.

307
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:41,640
Sa ne uitam in jur sa
vedem ce ne ofera
azi lumea:

308
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:44,520
Nesiguranta,
instabilitate.

309
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:47,920
Biserica trebuie
sa devin iar un
protagonist,

310
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:51,560
Trebuie sa propuna
evenimente minunate,

311
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:55,400
...Ca al nostru,
o npua Confirmare,
reinnoita.

312
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:59,120
Si crucifixul va fi
darul comunitatii
noastre.

313
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:03,720
-E un crucifix
figurativ.
-Da,trebuie sa
facem crucifixul

314
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:06,360
Inainte sa vina
episcopul.

315
00:37:06,560 --> 00:37:10,680
-Dumineca dimineata.
-E destul timp?

316
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:14,920
-Nu pot inainte.
-Nu poate inainte.

317
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:20,560
La 3 Confirmarea,
Sfanta Slujba si
prezentarea
crucifixului...

318
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:24,720
-Cristiano,hai aici.
-La 5,dansul micilor
virgine...

319
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:29,640
Le trebuie o
bataie buna!

320
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:32,000
Copiii trebuie
sa se supuna.

321
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:38,880
Sa se supuna in
numele cui?

322
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,640
Calmati-va.

323
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,880
Ma-ntorc imediat.

324
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:57,200
De unde ia el
crucifixul?

325
00:37:57,400 --> 00:38:02,360
E o biserica in ruine
in orasul parintelui
Mario.

326
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:09,760
-Cum se numea
exercitiul ala!
-"Aliniera pentru
Domnul".

327
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:12,400
Cand va fi?

328
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:15,760
Excelent,pentru
Confirmare.

329
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:20,040
Nu,imi pare rau,
nu pot ininte.

330
00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:24,560
70,toti oameni e
incredere,

331
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:27,000
Nu va faceti griji.

332
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:31,880
Despre celalalt lucru,
spune-i Excelentei
sale ca ma simt
gata...

333
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:36,840
Si-as putea da mai
mult daca as fi
transferat.

334
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:39,320
-Auziti?
-Ce?

335
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:44,080
-Il transfera.
-Ce-nseamna asta?

336
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:49,080
-Asa a spus,vrea o
biserica mai mare.
-De ce?

337
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:51,960
Intr-o biaerica
mai importanta...

338
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:55,120
Poate fi facut
episcop.

339
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:57,920
E bine pentru cariera
lui chiar,daca nu
se roaga bine.

340
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:13,600
"Acum,Doamne,lasa-ti
robul sa mearga in
pace,dupa vorba ta."

341
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:17,280
"Pentru ochii mei..."

342
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:23,480
"...Am vazut mantuirea
ta,pe care-Ai faut-o
la toate popoarele"

343
00:40:23,680 --> 00:40:26,120
"O lumina pentru
revelatia
meamurilor..."

344
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:41,640
"...Si glorie pentru
poporul lui Israel."

345
00:40:43,520 --> 00:40:48,000
"Salveaza-na in
veghe,nu ne lasa
in somn..."

346
00:40:57,720 --> 00:41:00,400
Am luat mancarea
pentru careva
zile.

347
00:41:37,480 --> 00:41:40,960
-E adevarat ca veti
fi transferat?
-As vrea!

348
00:41:42,120 --> 00:41:44,320
Cum adica "As vrea"?
Si eu?

349
00:41:44,520 --> 00:41:49,320
Chiar daca voi fi
transferat,nu voi
uita niciodata
comunitatea.

350
00:41:49,520 --> 00:41:53,280
Si ar trebui sa fiti
bucurosi ca mi s-a
dat o asa mare
responsabilitate.

351
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,480
Stiu asta.

352
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:59,880
Dar cine stie pe
cine vor trimite
in locul dv.

353
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:03,200
Poate vreun parinte
strain.

354
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:10,920
E trziu,te asteapta
acasa.

355
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:14,440
Am adus cearsafuri,
ma duc sa schimb
patul.

356
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:30,680
-Mancati?
-Nu,multumesc.

357
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:26,840
Uite!

358
00:43:28,120 --> 00:43:30,880
O sa-ti cada in cap.

359
00:43:37,400 --> 00:43:39,760
-Sa mergem la mare.
-Mm?

360
00:43:39,960 --> 00:43:42,640
-Sa mergem la mare.
-As vrea sa pot!
-Dar ai spus?

361
00:43:42,840 --> 00:43:46,280
-Hai,te rog.
-Pe jos?

362
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:49,280
-Da.
-Nu.

363
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:52,440
-Nu.
-Hai!

364
00:43:55,160 --> 00:43:58,080
-Buna seara.
-Buna seara.
Chiria!

365
00:44:02,400 --> 00:44:04,320
Pot?

366
00:44:04,520 --> 00:44:08,240
-Fata noastre!
-Sunt aici.

367
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:11,200
Scuzati-ma,e dezordine.

368
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:13,200
Mancati,sa vin
mai tarziu?

369
00:44:13,400 --> 00:44:16,560
Nu,nicio problema,
programul nostru
nu e fix.

370
00:44:16,760 --> 00:44:18,720
-Poftiti.
-Multumesc.

371
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:22,480
Asta-i chiria.

372
00:44:30,320 --> 00:44:32,680
-Totul e bine?
-Da.

373
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:38,920
-Si cum e la serviciu?
-Bine.

374
00:44:39,120 --> 00:44:41,400
Macar e un serviciu.

375
00:44:41,600 --> 00:44:45,480
Ar fi perfect daca
n-ar incepe asa de
dimineata.

376
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:49,280
Fiecare serviciu are
dezavantajele lui.

377
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:51,040
Si-al meu e un
serviciu,dar
sarcina e prea
mare.

378
00:44:51,240 --> 00:44:54,120
Trebuie sa va
protejez...

379
00:44:54,320 --> 00:44:56,880
...Sa actionmez in
numele parohiei.

380
00:44:57,080 --> 00:45:01,360
De aceea vreau sa
stiu daca ma pot
baza pe dv.,

381
00:45:01,560 --> 00:45:03,320
Pe familia voastra.

382
00:45:03,520 --> 00:45:05,720
Nu sunt vremuri
bune,

383
00:45:05,920 --> 00:45:09,840
Sunt asa de multi
oameni rai prin jur.

384
00:45:11,360 --> 00:45:14,040
-Alegerile!
-Desigur.

385
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:20,800
-Ce trebuie sa fac?
-Semnati aici,

386
00:45:21,720 --> 00:45:23,640
Numele si prenumele.

387
00:45:24,840 --> 00:45:27,400
-Numele:Ventura.
-Da.

388
00:45:30,800 --> 00:45:32,880
Ventura Rita.

389
00:45:33,080 --> 00:45:35,240
Poftiti.

390
00:45:35,440 --> 00:45:37,600
-Aici?
-Da.

391
00:45:40,400 --> 00:45:42,800
-Cealalta fiica?
-Rosa?

392
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:45,640
-Are 18 ani?
-Da,aproape.

393
00:45:50,120 --> 00:45:54,360
-Rosetta!
-Ce-i?
-Hai aici!

394
00:45:59,480 --> 00:46:01,720
Ce-i? Am de invatat.

395
00:46:01,920 --> 00:46:03,960
Numele si prenumele.

396
00:46:05,960 --> 00:46:08,640
Veti vota la scoala
primara in Via
Manzoni,

397
00:46:08,840 --> 00:46:12,400
La sectoa B.

398
00:46:13,240 --> 00:46:15,040
Asa cred.

399
00:46:16,600 --> 00:46:21,720
Asta-i candidatul
pe care-l votati.

400
00:46:24,400 --> 00:46:26,120
Si pentru tine.

401
00:46:44,640 --> 00:46:48,800
-Doamna Agata,totul
e bine?
-Da,intrati,va rog.

402
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:51,360
-Ati rezolvat
problema aia?
-Da.

403
00:46:55,200 --> 00:46:58,040
Sara,incepe mai
din spate.

404
00:46:59,840 --> 00:47:02,080
Destul de departe,
acum hai in fata.

405
00:47:03,600 --> 00:47:05,760
Sara,stai drept..

406
00:47:05,960 --> 00:47:08,560
Te duci spre Domnul!

407
00:47:09,640 --> 00:47:11,840
Copii...

408
00:47:13,040 --> 00:47:16,560
Confirmarea e lupta
noastra spirituala,

409
00:47:16,760 --> 00:47:19,560
Acum sunteti soldatii
lui Cristos.

410
00:47:19,760 --> 00:47:22,480
Aratati toti ca
mumiile!

411
00:47:22,680 --> 00:47:24,680
Hai,hai in fata!

412
00:47:26,120 --> 00:47:28,120
Stai,formula.

413
00:47:28,320 --> 00:47:32,000
Sirit Sfant,ma incred
in tine.

414
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:34,640
Eli,eli...

415
00:47:35,680 --> 00:47:39,560
-Eli,eli,lema
sabachthani.
-Bravo.Ce inseamna?

416
00:47:39,760 --> 00:47:42,280
Sunt cuvintele
Domnului,Marta.

417
00:47:42,480 --> 00:47:45,760
-Dar ce inseamna?
-Nu-i momentul.

418
00:47:45,960 --> 00:47:47,320
Sara,continua.

419
00:47:47,520 --> 00:47:51,600
Ma incred in tine
asa cum apa curge
din fata marii.

420
00:47:51,800 --> 00:47:55,280
Elibereaza-ma de
toate pacatele,
iarta-ma si da-mi...

421
00:47:55,480 --> 00:47:59,240
Energie,Sara!
Energie!

422
00:48:00,760 --> 00:48:03,040
Gandeste-te la Rambo,
il stii?

423
00:48:04,680 --> 00:48:06,520
Hai!

424
00:48:06,720 --> 00:48:08,480
Continua.

425
00:48:08,680 --> 00:48:10,520
O pisica!

426
00:48:11,880 --> 00:48:14,280
Flavia,a intrat
o pisica.

427
00:48:18,720 --> 00:48:20,840
Copii,prindeti-o!

428
00:48:21,040 --> 00:48:23,120
Natale!

429
00:48:25,240 --> 00:48:27,720
Bine,Marta.Prinde-o!

430
00:48:28,520 --> 00:48:30,760
Asa.

431
00:48:30,960 --> 00:48:33,440
Nu,copii...

432
00:48:54,720 --> 00:48:57,640
D-ra Marta Ventura,
hai cu mine.

433
00:49:08,160 --> 00:49:10,160
Formula.

434
00:49:13,200 --> 00:49:17,600
Spirit Sfant,in
momente grele
te caut.

435
00:49:19,480 --> 00:49:22,560
-Da-mi frica de
Dumnezeu...
-Crezi in Dumnezu...

436
00:49:22,760 --> 00:49:26,920
...In Tatal,stapan
al cerului si-al
pamantului,a tot
ce exista?

437
00:49:29,720 --> 00:49:31,440
Cred.

438
00:49:31,640 --> 00:49:34,960
Crezi in Spiritul
Sfant,care-i Domnul
si da viata,

439
00:49:35,160 --> 00:49:38,800
Sfintei Biserici
Catolice,credinta
sfintilor,

440
00:49:39,000 --> 00:49:42,200
Iertarea pacatelor
si invierea trupului

441
00:49:42,400 --> 00:49:44,320
Si-n viata eterna?

442
00:49:49,400 --> 00:49:51,920
Cred! Cred!

443
00:49:52,120 --> 00:49:56,440
E credinta noastra,
credinta bisericii
noastre...

444
00:49:56,640 --> 00:50:01,040
...Si avem cinstea
sa profesam asta de
la Iisus Cristos,
Domnul nostru.Amin!

445
00:50:01,240 --> 00:50:03,480
In momentul asta,
episcopul te va
marca c-o cruce...

446
00:50:03,680 --> 00:50:06,440
...Si-o sa-ti dea
o palma simbolica,
cam asa!

447
00:51:07,200 --> 00:51:12,080
Cand cresc vreau
sa fiu sfant,ca
toti sa-mi dea
daruri.

448
00:51:18,040 --> 00:51:20,200
Vrei un dar?

449
00:51:38,760 --> 00:51:41,160
Iti dau parul meu.

450
00:51:42,440 --> 00:51:45,760
-Taie-l.
-Nu stiu cum.

451
00:51:46,680 --> 00:51:48,520
Incearca.

452
00:51:48,720 --> 00:51:51,000
Taie-l.

453
00:51:51,200 --> 00:51:53,080
Taie-l.

454
00:51:54,040 --> 00:51:56,720
Apoi il poti lega
de-al tau.

455
00:52:31,480 --> 00:52:33,360
Nu pot.

456
00:52:51,440 --> 00:52:53,280
Tine.

457
00:53:25,560 --> 00:53:29,280
-Cum sa-l leg?
-Uite,ti-ai murdarit
toate hainele!

458
00:53:29,480 --> 00:53:32,280
De unde ai asta?

459
00:53:33,360 --> 00:53:35,760
Nu vreau sa vad.

460
00:53:39,600 --> 00:53:42,080
Ce-ai facut?

461
00:53:44,920 --> 00:53:47,240
Te dai mare.

462
00:53:48,480 --> 00:53:51,200
-Sa mergem la frizer.
-Nu,ramane asa.

463
00:53:51,400 --> 00:53:54,960
Vrea sa fie observata.

464
00:53:55,160 --> 00:53:59,080
-Haideti amandoua.
-Ce-ai facut?

465
00:54:03,640 --> 00:54:05,120
Debby,sa mergem!

466
00:54:11,320 --> 00:54:14,160
Poate mai bine sa
nu iau Confirmarea.

467
00:54:21,600 --> 00:54:24,640
Marta,Nu mai face
probleme,te rog.

468
00:54:31,080 --> 00:54:33,040
Stai.

469
00:54:49,600 --> 00:54:52,120
Aveai dreptate
sa-l tai.

470
00:54:54,120 --> 00:54:56,200
Va creste mai des.

471
00:55:02,040 --> 00:55:04,120
Dupa Confirmare
o sa mergem la
mare.

472
00:55:11,400 --> 00:55:13,640
Frumos.

473
00:55:17,360 --> 00:55:20,240
Ca o mireasa!
Si parul tau...

474
00:55:20,440 --> 00:55:22,000
E un obicei in
tara ta?

475
00:55:22,200 --> 00:55:25,880
Ziua cea mare e aici,

476
00:55:26,080 --> 00:55:29,280
Totul trebuie
sa fie perfect.

477
00:55:29,480 --> 00:55:33,000
Tu,du-te si agata
asta pe hol.

478
00:55:33,200 --> 00:55:35,640
Tu ai grija de mese.

479
00:55:35,840 --> 00:55:40,320
Tu intinde covorul
si ai grija de
scena.

480
00:55:40,520 --> 00:55:43,720
Tu du-te in magazie
si adu decoratiile.

481
00:55:43,920 --> 00:55:45,760
Hai,draga.Du-te.

482
00:55:49,280 --> 00:55:51,800
-Nu.
-Sub perdeaua rosie?

483
00:55:54,440 --> 00:55:56,480
Nu,poate acolo..

484
00:55:56,680 --> 00:55:58,600
Muta lucrurile.

485
00:56:12,240 --> 00:56:14,440
Ce-ai gasit?

486
00:56:34,240 --> 00:56:36,720
-Oh,nu!
-Ii vreau!

487
00:56:36,920 --> 00:56:39,320
-Hai!
-Nu!

488
00:56:39,520 --> 00:56:44,240
-Sunt draguti.Ce
sa facem cu ei?
-Sa-i ducem acasa.

489
00:56:44,440 --> 00:56:48,480
Nici gand,trebuie
sa-i inecam!

490
00:56:48,680 --> 00:56:52,520
Bunicul ii pune in
saci si ii fierbe.

491
00:56:52,720 --> 00:56:55,680
-Te fierbem pe
tine,nu pe pisoi!
-Atunci pune-i
jos,ii doare.

492
00:56:55,880 --> 00:56:57,720
Ce se-ntampla?

493
00:56:57,920 --> 00:57:00,920
Nu-i atinge,poarta
boli.

494
00:57:01,120 --> 00:57:03,040
-Hai,afara.
-Ce boli?

495
00:57:03,240 --> 00:57:06,560
De toate felutile!
Afara,toti!

496
00:57:06,760 --> 00:57:10,160
Si tu,nu-i atinge,
iesi de aici

497
00:57:12,280 --> 00:57:15,440
Gennaro,cheama-l pe
Ignazio,te rog!

498
00:57:15,640 --> 00:57:17,480
Ignazio!

499
01:00:29,480 --> 01:00:33,160
Hai!

500
01:00:44,240 --> 01:00:46,120
Ce faci aici?

501
01:00:54,920 --> 01:00:57,480
Asta nu duce nicaieri.

502
01:01:46,200 --> 01:01:48,320
Marta,nu-i asa?

503
01:01:50,280 --> 01:01:52,040
Totul e bine?

504
01:01:53,200 --> 01:01:56,400
Ce faci aici?
Ar trebui sa
fii gata.

505
01:02:20,760 --> 01:02:23,240
Intrarea...

506
01:02:24,720 --> 01:02:26,760
Da,Marta.

507
01:02:28,680 --> 01:02:30,400
Gandeste-te.

508
01:02:45,120 --> 01:02:48,680
-Cum ai ajuns aici?
-Pe jos.

509
01:02:48,880 --> 01:02:51,640
Pe jos.

510
01:02:54,200 --> 01:02:56,320
Santa? Nimeni...

511
01:02:56,520 --> 01:02:59,080
Mobilul mamei sale?

512
01:03:00,160 --> 01:03:02,680
Inteleg.Bine.

513
01:03:09,960 --> 01:03:13,480
-Urca in masina.
-Nu,multumesc.
Ma duc singura.

514
01:03:13,680 --> 01:03:16,240
-Urca in masina!
-Ma duceam acasa.

515
01:03:16,440 --> 01:03:18,480
Nu-i nimeni.

516
01:03:18,680 --> 01:03:20,480
Stai.

517
01:03:25,760 --> 01:03:30,280
-Poti sa-mi spui
ce faceai?
-Ma plimbam.

518
01:03:30,480 --> 01:03:33,640
Te plimbai.Pe
autostrada?

519
01:03:44,160 --> 01:03:47,560
Oricum,aveam nevoie
de ajutor.

520
01:03:48,720 --> 01:03:51,000
-Unde mergem?
-La un sat din
apropiere.

521
01:03:52,680 --> 01:03:54,880
Satul in care
m-am nascut.

522
01:03:55,960 --> 01:03:58,520
Mergm sa aducem
crucifixul.

523
01:04:01,960 --> 01:04:03,880
Suntem intr-o
misiune.

524
01:04:28,000 --> 01:04:30,200
Asteapta-ma in
masina.

525
01:04:38,000 --> 01:04:41,440
Participarea voastra
arata credinta...

526
01:04:41,640 --> 01:04:46,200
...In comunitatea
noastra..

527
01:04:46,880 --> 01:04:49,800
-Multumesc.
-Viata lunga
parintelui Mario!

528
01:04:53,120 --> 01:04:55,200
Sa incepem,

529
01:04:55,400 --> 01:04:56,760
Muzica!

530
01:04:56,960 --> 01:05:00,160
Pentru semnaturi,
aici.

531
01:05:02,600 --> 01:05:05,800
-Sunt doar o mana.
-E gripa pe aici.

532
01:05:08,000 --> 01:05:09,960
Multumesc.

533
01:05:21,320 --> 01:05:23,000
Multumesc.

534
01:05:29,640 --> 01:05:31,880
Intelegi cand iti
spun?

535
01:05:32,080 --> 01:05:35,200
Daca iti spun sa
astepti in masina,
e un motivn.

536
01:05:48,360 --> 01:05:51,520
Alo? Da,e cu mine.

537
01:05:53,760 --> 01:05:55,960
Ce trebuia sa
fi facut?

538
01:05:57,720 --> 01:05:59,920
Sa?

539
01:06:02,040 --> 01:06:07,640
-Eli,eli,lema
sabachthani.
-Da,stiu,n-am
sa obosesc.

540
01:06:07,840 --> 01:06:12,840
-Eli,eli,lema,
sabachthani.
-Tineti-ma la
curent.

541
01:06:15,720 --> 01:06:18,840
-Vreti sa mancati
ceva?
-Nu,mersi.Asteptam
mai multi oameni.

542
01:06:19,240 --> 01:06:21,320
-Sunt aici doar
pentru semnaturi.
-Sigur.

543
01:06:21,520 --> 01:06:24,080
Ceva dulce pentru
fetita?

544
01:06:24,360 --> 01:06:26,800
-Un biban frumos?
-15 minute,
nu mai mult.

545
01:06:29,000 --> 01:06:30,960
Pregateste-l.

546
01:06:31,400 --> 01:06:33,720
-Doamna Angela...
-Bun venit.

547
01:06:33,920 --> 01:06:37,280
Nu vreau sa deranjez,
dar as vrea un favor.

548
01:06:37,480 --> 01:06:40,600
Rugati-va pentru
sora mea,are o
boala ce nu
cedeaza.

549
01:06:40,800 --> 01:06:43,680
Ma rog asa de tare.

550
01:06:43,880 --> 01:06:47,560
Va puteti ruga si
dv. pentru ea?

551
01:06:47,760 --> 01:06:50,520
-Desigur.
-Fotografia ei.

552
01:06:50,720 --> 01:06:54,000
-O cheama Caterina.
-Mama?
-Stai putin...

553
01:06:54,200 --> 01:06:57,400
-Sarutati-o.
-Caterina.

554
01:06:58,960 --> 01:07:01,960
-Am sa ma rog
pentru sora ta.
- Multumesc,paritne
Mario.

555
01:07:02,160 --> 01:07:06,560
-Scuzat-o,stit-i cum
e.Dar gateste bine.
-Stiu.

556
01:07:17,880 --> 01:07:20,800
-Nu mananci?
-Nu mananc peste.

557
01:07:21,000 --> 01:07:22,480
Pacat.

558
01:07:22,680 --> 01:07:25,240
Stii cat calciu
contine?

559
01:07:43,520 --> 01:07:45,720
Nu,stai aici.

560
01:07:57,880 --> 01:08:00,920
Marta,cum de te-ai
murdarit?

561
01:09:05,040 --> 01:09:07,320
D-ra?

562
01:09:08,040 --> 01:09:10,680
-Ocupat.
-Totul e bine?

563
01:09:11,560 --> 01:09:14,120
Ia asta.

564
01:09:24,200 --> 01:09:26,440
E prima data,huh?

565
01:09:29,880 --> 01:09:34,440
E un lucru bun,
cgiar daca pare
rau.

566
01:11:08,640 --> 01:11:11,040
Am nevoie la
toaleta.

567
01:11:20,480 --> 01:11:23,520
Poti merge unde
vrei,nu-i niciun
om aici.Bine?

568
01:11:23,720 --> 01:11:25,800
Te asteptam la
biserica.

569
01:13:13,760 --> 01:13:16,520
Ce faci? Lasa-l!

570
01:13:38,920 --> 01:13:41,280
Nu te-am recunoscut.

571
01:13:42,680 --> 01:13:45,240
In zilele astea
n-am vazut prea
bine.

572
01:13:57,680 --> 01:14:01,040
Il duc departe,la
caldura si siguranta.

573
01:14:01,240 --> 01:14:04,520
Ai vazut starea
in care l-ai
lasat s-ajunga?

574
01:14:07,720 --> 01:14:10,120
Alo?

575
01:14:10,320 --> 01:14:12,920
-Cum esti?
-Bine.

576
01:14:17,240 --> 01:14:20,840
-Stai,unde te duci?
-Am intarziat,trebuie
sa le dau de stire.

577
01:14:25,720 --> 01:14:27,720
Alo,Santa?

578
01:14:43,880 --> 01:14:45,960
Sunteti preot?

579
01:14:47,000 --> 01:14:48,920
Da.

580
01:14:52,120 --> 01:14:55,320
-Studiati ca si
preotii?
-Da.

581
01:15:03,360 --> 01:15:07,040
Ce inseamna "eli,eli,
lema sabachthani"?

582
01:15:09,080 --> 01:15:10,600
"Eli,eli..."

583
01:15:13,440 --> 01:15:15,880
E un strigat,

584
01:15:16,080 --> 01:15:17,960
E strigatul lui
Iisus...

585
01:15:19,560 --> 01:15:22,800
"Doamne,de ce m-ai
parasit?"

586
01:15:25,520 --> 01:15:28,240
-De ce striga?
-Pentru ca e
manios.

587
01:15:32,600 --> 01:15:34,440
Cum ti-l imaginezi?

588
01:15:36,000 --> 01:15:38,240
-Bun.
-Zambitor?

589
01:15:39,720 --> 01:15:42,680
-Da.
-Cu ochi albastri?

590
01:15:44,520 --> 01:15:46,400
Gata sa te
imbratiseze?

591
01:15:48,040 --> 01:15:51,640
-Da.
-Dar e manios,
furios.

592
01:15:52,880 --> 01:15:56,440
E singur,alergand
dintr-un loc in
altul.

593
01:15:58,520 --> 01:16:02,160
Peste tot ii cer
sa vindece,sa
faca miracole...

594
01:16:03,280 --> 01:16:04,840
...Si alearga
catre toti.

595
01:16:07,680 --> 01:16:11,280
Cu discipolii
ingnoranti din
jurul sau.

596
01:16:11,480 --> 01:16:14,480
...Ce nu inteleg
nimic,si ii cer
mereu explicatii.

597
01:16:14,680 --> 01:16:17,400
N-au o farama de
imaginatie.

598
01:16:20,000 --> 01:16:22,240
Si sunt socati.

599
01:16:39,920 --> 01:16:41,520
Citeste.

600
01:16:46,520 --> 01:16:50,200
"Cand familia lui
aude asta,s-au dus
sa-l opreasca..."

601
01:16:50,400 --> 01:16:53,440
"...Pentru c-au spus:
Si-a pierdut mintile."

602
01:17:21,880 --> 01:17:25,240
-E aici.
-Cine?
-Episcopul.

603
01:17:25,440 --> 01:17:27,480
Acum ce facem?

604
01:17:27,680 --> 01:17:30,720
N-ar fi trebuit sa
astepte pana-n
iltimul moment sa
aduca crucifixul.

605
01:17:30,920 --> 01:17:33,960
-A avut alte treburi.
-Si acum ce facem?

606
01:17:34,160 --> 01:17:38,280
Parem o parohie
dezorganizata,
neserioasa.

607
01:17:38,480 --> 01:17:42,200
-As spune...
-Sa incepem
cu dansul.

608
01:20:14,480 --> 01:20:16,960
Marta,hai sa mergem!

609
01:20:29,760 --> 01:20:31,760
Ajuta-ma.

610
01:22:25,360 --> 01:22:28,000
-Buna.
- Hello, dear.

611
01:22:28,200 --> 01:22:31,200
-Ea e mama.
-Buna,doamna.
-Buna ziua.

612
01:22:31,400 --> 01:22:34,640
-Cu placere,Santa.
-Marta?

613
01:22:35,680 --> 01:22:38,920
Nu ti-a spus?

614
01:22:39,120 --> 01:22:43,440
Parintele Mario a
ales-o pentru o
treaba foarte
importanta,

615
01:22:43,640 --> 01:22:48,080
S-au dus impreuna
sa aduca noul
crucifix.

616
01:22:48,280 --> 01:22:50,960
Cand? Nu mi-a
spus nimic.

617
01:22:51,160 --> 01:22:53,800
Nu stiu.Imi pare rau.

618
01:23:04,360 --> 01:23:06,240
Luati,va rog.

619
01:23:09,600 --> 01:23:13,680
Nu vreti sa veniti?
E dansul micilor
virgine....

620
01:23:13,880 --> 01:23:17,120
...Am organizat
multe lucruri
dragute.

621
01:23:19,440 --> 01:23:22,080
Atunci ma duc,ma
cheama datoria.

622
01:23:27,240 --> 01:23:30,040
Pot sa intreb ceva?

623
01:23:30,240 --> 01:23:33,800
Unde va fi transferat
parintele Mario?

624
01:23:34,920 --> 01:23:37,640
Ce-i cu intrebarea
asta ciudata?

625
01:23:37,840 --> 01:23:42,600
De vreme ce e un
anumit grad de
familiaritate
intre noi,

626
01:23:42,800 --> 01:23:47,520
Mi-a spus ca poate
va fi transferat
la o parohie
importanta.

627
01:23:47,720 --> 01:23:49,760
Doamna,cine sunteti?

628
01:23:51,280 --> 01:23:56,240
-Santa!
-Dar ce sunteti
pentru Sfanta
noastra Biserica?

629
01:23:57,560 --> 01:23:59,680
Ce reprezentati?

630
01:24:06,480 --> 01:24:11,160
-Excelenta-sa ar vrea
o batista.
-Ma duc imediat.

631
01:25:33,840 --> 01:25:36,640
Dupa Confirmare,
ce mai facem?

632
01:25:36,840 --> 01:25:40,040
Nimic,mergem in
biserica,atata tot.

633
01:25:44,160 --> 01:25:48,160
-Cititi Evanghelia?
-In fiecare zi,
la slujba.

634
01:25:49,440 --> 01:25:52,000
Stiti ce se spime
despre Iisus?

635
01:25:57,760 --> 01:26:00,760
-Ce se spune?
-A fost nebun.

636
01:26:01,560 --> 01:26:03,800
Prostii!

637
01:26:06,800 --> 01:26:10,080
Da,manios,furios.

638
01:27:42,120 --> 01:27:45,320
-Pot sa mananc?
-Da.
-O bucata.

639
01:27:53,560 --> 01:27:55,880
Parul ala lung!

640
01:29:00,000 --> 01:29:03,040
Iertat-ma,totul
e pregatit.

641
01:29:13,880 --> 01:29:18,440
Deci,te-ai hotarat?
Te transferi sau
ramai cu noi?

642
01:29:21,840 --> 01:29:24,000
Unde pot merge?

643
01:29:28,600 --> 01:29:30,680
E o pata.

644
01:29:35,760 --> 01:29:38,480
Totul e gata.

645
01:30:19,240 --> 01:30:22,360
Doare...m-am muscat.

646
01:30:22,560 --> 01:30:25,280
-Ce-ai facut?
-M-am muscat.

647
01:30:27,160 --> 01:30:30,520
-Era curioasa sa vad
crucifixul ala.
-Stiti ce s-a
intamplat?

648
01:30:30,720 --> 01:30:35,840
Fetita aia Marta
a taiat franghiile
si crucifixul a
cazut.

649
01:30:41,360 --> 01:30:44,400
Nu-mi calomnia sora.

650
01:31:14,280 --> 01:31:16,400
Frati si surori,

651
01:31:18,240 --> 01:31:22,960
Inainte de toate
imi cer scuze in
fata intregii
comunitati.

652
01:31:24,160 --> 01:31:30,680
Azi copiii nostri cresc.

653
01:31:33,000 --> 01:31:36,760
Multumita
episcopului
nostru Giorgio,

654
01:31:36,960 --> 01:31:42,480
Care...

655
01:31:46,280 --> 01:31:48,240
Cu prezenta sa...

656
01:34:00,800 --> 01:34:03,160
Vrei sa vezi un
miracol?

657
01:34:06,000 --> 01:34:07,560
Uite.

658
01:34:12,800 --> 01:34:14,840
E inca viu.


